Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:03.69,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H4C4095&\fs13\frz141.9\fax-0.3\3c&HD6DFDE&\bord2\pos(309.76,294.833)}Recruiting part-time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.04,0:00:08.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A melancholy Monday has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.24,0:00:15.45,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Feels good to be over your cold, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.45,0:00:16.48,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:21.20,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you happy your cold \Nlet you miss school a few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.20,0:00:22.84,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.84,0:00:24.07,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:26.41,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,You always say you wanna stay home...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:28.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like going to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.12,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but for someone like me, \Neven one day of failing to attend class
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.12,0:00:34.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,puts me in risk of being \Nforgotten by my classmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:38.19,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you're a real pain \Nin your own ass, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:41.77,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and Mom says it's time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.65,0:00:44.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:48.76,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I could burst from the sheer volume \Nof nuisance I inflict upon myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.02,0:00:51.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.68,0:00:54.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I joined a band, and I'm \Nworking part-time at a club!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:01:00.09,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps I've graduated from my introversion!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.84,0:01:02.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.66,0:01:04.60,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my guitar to school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.60,0:01:07.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's bound to talk to me this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.54,0:01:15.63,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Putting the onus on \Nothers fails once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.79,0:01:14.10,DefaultTop,Classmate B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you watch the latest Oto-Station?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.10,0:01:15.63,DefaultTop,Classmate A,0000,0000,0000,,I did did!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:19.50,Default,Classmate A,0000,0000,0000,,You can stream BAKWIMPS again!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.50,0:01:21.62,Default,Classmate B,0000,0000,0000,,I've been listening to them\Nso much since yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:23.55,Default,Classmate B,0000,0000,0000,,they're still playing in my head!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.55,0:01:24.52,Default,Classmate A,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.52,0:01:25.77,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Band talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:29.49,Default,Classmate A,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.49,0:01:32.48,Default,Classmate B,0000,0000,0000,,You hardly ever talk to anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,All my preparation assumed \Nothers would approach me first,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.93,0:01:37.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't know how \Nto start a conversation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.26,0:01:39.64,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.64,0:01:41.05,Default,Classmates A & B,0000,0000,0000,,In that short a time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.05,0:01:42.29,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,It's lunchtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:48.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,This is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.95,0:01:51.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd managed to talk to them, \Nright about now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.76,0:01:54.72,Default,Classmate A,0000,0000,0000,,Barging into our convo like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.72,0:01:57.19,Default,Classmate A,0000,0000,0000,,Was she listening in the \Nwhole time or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:59.93,Default,Classmate B,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know she was such a creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:02.33,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely how it'd be!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never rise above my station again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.04,0:02:05.77,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll live under the radar forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:08.39,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.65,0:02:15.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Still... A quiet place like this \Nis just perfect for lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:17.85,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I found a nice spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.85,0:02:20.14,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's awkward eating all alone\Nin the classroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:24.69,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And once I become a popular guitarist, \NI'll go on Oto-Station and say...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.12,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,What were you like in high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.12,0:02:31.34,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any friends back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.34,0:02:36.55,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I often ate lunch in a dark corner \Nfilled with desks and janitorial supplies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:41.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can awe people with how much \NI've changed! Y'know how it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.01,0:02:43.43,DefaultTop,Girl Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Karaoke was so much fun the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:43.43,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,People!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.93,DefaultTop,Girl Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan's such a great singer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.03,DefaultTop,Girl Student A,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she played guitar in a band before she quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.44,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H1A1F1C&\fnComic Sans MS\3c&HFBFFFD&\bord2.5\b0\pos(317.725,285)}Kids, don't try this at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.03,0:02:51.92,DefaultTop,Girl Student B,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Now that's musical talent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:50.14,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Band?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Nijika-chan was talking \Nabout wanting a new guitar-slash-vocalist...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.49,0:02:57.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Since my cold kept me from \Nworking for a few days,
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.03,0:03:01.11,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I must find a guitar-slash-vocalist \Nto prove my commitment to Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:01.66,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,646)\fs20\fnArial Black\c&H4E76E2&\3c&H000000&\bord0.6\frz13\frx7\fax0.15\pos(298.382,32.768)}Kessoku Band
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:01.66,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,646)\fnArial Black\c&H4E76E2&\3c&H000000&\bord1.2\frz13\frx7\fax0.12\pos(318.294,137.526)}Now Recruiting Guitar/Vocalist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:01.66,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,646)\fnComic Sans MS\fs22\b0\c&H00112C&\3c&H3091D0&\bord3.5\frz13\frx7\fax0.15\pos(339.342,189.962)}Even newbies can come and learn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:01.66,Box Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,646)\fs30\fnComic Sans MS\c&H6B64CE&\3c&H58EFE1&\bord1.5\fax0.12\frz13\frx7\pos(346.167,246.379)}Please!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:03:01.66,Box Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,646)\fs14\fnComic Sans MS\c&H4F8B89&\3c&H64F2E3&\bord1.5\frz13\frx7\fax0.12\pos(371.2,274.361)}Please contact STARRY staff
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.45,0:03:05.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But the thought of going up \Nto a total stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.79,Default,Girl Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.79,0:03:08.33,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Heya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.53,DefaultTop,Girl Student A,0000,0000,0000,,I'm super sorry, but I have \Na huge favor to ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:11.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of girl is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.53,0:03:12.88,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.84,DefaultTop,Girl Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind pitching in at \Nour basketball game next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:17.42,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.33,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,280)}She's super nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:23.93,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord4\c&H1A1F1C&\fnComic Sans MS\3c&HFBFFFD&\b0\pos(317.725,319.692)}Kids, don't try this at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:21.65,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll land a three-pointer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:23.93,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,280)}She's pretty, and athletic, and popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.65,0:03:23.93,DefaultTop,Girl Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}and{\i1} she plays the guitar...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:29.56,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm supposed to issue an \Ninvitation to someone like {\i0}her{\i1}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.94,0:03:32.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, my identity...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:35.69,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My entire identity is crumbling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.77,0:03:37.15,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(695,1)\fnArial Black\fs32\an8\c&H8065E5&\3c&HE2CEE8&\bord3\pos(451.413,17.393)}Identity
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:37.73,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Pwip.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.35,0:03:40.99,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:56.43,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked dark, cramped spaces,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.80,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd bury my face deep in my hood
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:04:01.18,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes resented the heartless world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:04.93,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,but yearned for love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:11.57,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked being soaked by the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.57,0:04:13.94,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,because my face looked better clouded over
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.94,0:04:16.58,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended to be afraid of the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.58,0:04:19.41,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,while waiting for the sky to burst
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:26.37,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum through the light's distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:30.79,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make thunder roar
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.79,0:04:36.59,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum beyond the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.59,0:04:40.72,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:46.78,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum in a harmonizing quartet
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.78,0:04:50.77,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cause a revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:56.78,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum in a lamenting forte
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:05:01.53,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.83,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&H4800BE&\fnImpact\fs30\pos(238.5,132.5)}BOCCHI THE ROCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:09.83,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(485,1)\c&H4800BE&\fnComic Sans MS\fs26\b1\pos(416.5,255)}#3 Be Right There
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:18.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I worked up the courage \Nto arrive at her classroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:19.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but my mental fortitude lags behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:22.05,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You're Gotoh-san from Class 2, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:24.05,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She knows my n—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.05,0:05:26.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for someone in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.90,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Say it, Hitori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:35.31,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(822,935)\fnArial Black\fs32\c&H070F0C&\pos(360.391,90.095)\fax0.1}Band Is Looking For \NA Guitar/Vocalist
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.90,0:05:33.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,"My band is looking for a guitar-slash-\Nvocalist. Would you be interested?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:37.14,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ba! Gui! Vo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:37.14,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\fs40\fax0.1\bord4\c&H4137D2&\3c&H59D6EB&\pos(549.262,167.441)\fscy10\t(147,272,\fscy100)}Ba
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.14,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\fs40\fax0.1\bord4\c&H4137D2&\3c&H59D6EB&\pos(161.28,227.157)\fscy10\t(151,272,\fscy100)}Gui
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.69,0:05:37.14,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\fs40\fax0.1\bord4\c&H4137D2&\3c&H59D6EB&\pos(492.942,260.143)\fscy10\t(147,272,\fscy100)}Vo
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.65,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,She became a human beatbox!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.80,0:05:42.82,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.24,0:05:47.03,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Bam-chika-boom-chika... \Nbam-chika-boom-chika...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:50.70,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I... I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.83,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:59.69,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Two more additions to \Nmy dark past in one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:03.36,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:07.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,This is my new song: Double Dark Past, \NBocchi Acoustic Version.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.74,0:06:15.97,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Melancholy days, multiplying traumas
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.40,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna ditch this negative legacy I carry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:24.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The memories bring soft, \Nsecret tears to my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.53,0:06:27.55,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Mourning my past, so many dark mornings
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.55,0:06:31.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wishing, someday, \Nto just laugh it all away...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.75,0:06:36.00,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Begone, memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.87,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:39.12,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kita-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:40.17,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.89,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I got so worried when you ran off like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:44.28,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,but that was incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.36,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing at guitar, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.17,0:06:49.96,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That song you were playing \Nhad me totally enraptured!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.96,0:06:52.43,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She's saying nice things about me! \NWhat a nice person!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.81,0:06:54.36,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.18,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:58.69,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can you play other stuff? I wanna hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:07:01.94,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(402,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs32\c&H398BE6&\3c&H1C25C0&\bord2.5\pos(543.573,111.137)\frz337.9}Kit-aura
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.69,0:07:01.94,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The extrovert aura... It's so powerful, \NI can't look straight at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:05.44,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and you were trying to talk \Nto someone earlier, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.32,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This is my chance to invite her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:10.85,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, our band is actually \Nlooking for a guitar-slash-vocalist,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.72,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and I heard you played guitar, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.72,0:07:14.37,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.60,0:07:15.83,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.83,0:07:17.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Gotoh-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.24,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I can't join your band.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.37,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.37,0:07:24.16,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kind of a nerd, but the others are cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.16,0:07:26.59,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's not a problem with you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.46,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They're holding a barbecue next weekend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.59,0:07:28.46,DefaultTop,Nijika/Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They host a sports meet every six months!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.73,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They party in limousines after every gig!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.73,DefaultTop,Nijika/Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,This is the life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.43,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,They do so much cool stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.43,0:07:36.89,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want a band that parties {\i1}that{\i0} hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.05,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And... And...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.05,0:07:42.90,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I can't \Nactually play guitar at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I was in another band not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.21,0:07:49.38,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I lied when I joined because \NI wanted to get close to my senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:52.99,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But the whole thing was just \Nbeyond me, so I ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:54.92,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.92,0:07:55.87,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:08:00.91,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,There's more to playing than just \Nthis strum-strum stuff, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:04.16,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'd figured this wooden stick part \Nwas just for decoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.16,0:08:08.12,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's way too hard for someone \Nto learn on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:11.37,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,"Major chords"? "Minor"? \NWhat is this, baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.37,0:08:13.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Her non-comprehension \Nis on a whole other level!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:16.50,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone teach you to play, Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.49,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I mostly taught myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:20.78,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Really? That's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:22.50,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's not {\i1}that{\i0} great...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.97,0:08:26.87,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Will you teach me to play, Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:28.94,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You can be my teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:32.95,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You're so brilliant, I just know \Nyou'll get me through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:34.26,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.17,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I want to learn to play properly,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.17,0:08:39.76,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,go back to my old band, and apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.75,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So, when can you teach me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.88,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,After class, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:46.98,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've got a job at a club after class...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.98,0:08:49.25,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Then after work, maybe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:51.76,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a studio next door? \NWe can do it there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.63,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:56.42,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,V-Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:58.57,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.42,0:08:59.22,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so stupid?! Say no, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.56,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Can we start right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:01.68,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Certainly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.99,0:09:03.77,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Crap, crap, crap, crap, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:07.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotta get the girls \Nto act like party people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.00,0:09:11.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:12.99,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:18.20,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to work today blaring EDM and \Ndancing around with energy drinks on hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:21.22,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.16,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.82,0:09:27.12,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... You work in Shimo-Kitazawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.30,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You've been?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:32.00,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,My last band was in Shimo-Kita,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.00,0:09:35.02,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,and its members lived in the area, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.02,0:09:36.55,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.59,0:09:38.72,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.34,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You can't walk behind me! \NI don't know the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:44.16,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I'm still not \Nused to being here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:45.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.52,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one embarrassed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.42,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.42,0:09:52.29,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place called Starry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.29,0:09:55.78,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika-chan and Ryo-san \Nwill already be there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:59.66,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.47,0:10:01.66,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:02.24,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.34,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell you why, \Nbut that's the one place I can't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.60,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And you can never tell those people I was h—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:12.62,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Your instructions were super weird, \Nbut I bought energy drinks like you asked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.91,0:10:15.93,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The runaway guitarist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:22.18,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Runaway... guitarist?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.18,0:10:24.43,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:26.58,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,W-W-Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:28.65,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:35.63,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive my prior discourtesy! \NI'll do anything to make up for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:38.04,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I give you permission to rough me up good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:40.53,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Shh! You're gonna give people the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:42.87,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:45.66,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So you couldn't play guitar, Kita-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.93,0:10:46.83,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.83,0:10:50.37,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you always ditched practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.37,0:10:51.08,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.08,0:10:53.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Poor Kita-san seems so uncomfortable...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.03,0:10:55.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-If only I could think of \Nsomething nice to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:58.23,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We were worried when we didn't hear from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:10:59.63,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-san, so smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.23,0:10:59.63,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:05.26,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I assumed you were dead, so I've been \Nlighting incense for you every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.26,0:11:05.90,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,RIP.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.90,0:11:07.47,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty wild assumption...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:10.21,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Um... You aren't angry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:13.16,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I sorta blame ourselves \Nfor not catching on sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.16,0:11:13.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to work it out anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:20.60,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,S-Still, I feel too awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.74,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Please, let me make it up to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:24.66,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure how...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:27.97,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,How about you help out today at the club?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.67,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna be a busy night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.67,0:11:31.16,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That can't be enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:33.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,No, that'd be a huge help!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:34.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Please join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:35.73,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,If you'd like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.73,0:11:38.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad they worked it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:42.52,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,So, go over there and get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.52,0:11:43.64,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:53.59,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Manager have that outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.59,0:11:56.36,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,She's pretty darn good for a fill-in worker.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.36,0:11:58.96,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Kita-chan knows what she's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.96,0:12:00.18,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She really does!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:04.20,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,She'll give me extra time to slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:05.92,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it out of your pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:10.47,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,You smell good, Kita-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.47,0:12:12.28,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:15.30,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's the shampoo? It's my favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.28,0:12:15.30,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's never said {\i0}my{\i1} name before!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:18.27,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty outgoing, \NKita-chan. Wanna try reception?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.27,0:12:19.17,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:19.84,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:21.97,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And the job they've never trusted me with!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.25,0:12:24.03,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,500 yen for a drink ticket!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.03,0:12:26.66,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,What band did you come to see today?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.66,0:12:28.47,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Take a flyer, if you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.47,0:12:30.59,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Say, not bad at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.59,0:12:33.34,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I love interacting with people!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:35.11,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo always handles reception,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:37.32,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but her dead eyes are kind of a problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:38.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And her poker face can be scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:40.98,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-senpai looks fine just the way she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.98,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(525,1)\fs16\c&H8A95AB&\3c&HAFC3C4&\pos(397.368,53.583)}Trash
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.98,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(525,1)\fs16\c&H8B9095&\3c&HAFC3C4&\pos(509.439,58.815)}Recyclables
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:45.82,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,1724)\fnComic Sans MS\frz230\c&HCBFF59&\3c&H57B031&\bord2\blur2\pos(562.346,67.914)}Kita Kita\NKita Kita\NKita Kita
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.25,0:12:43.84,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi. What are you doing down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:47.24,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Losing my identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:48.88,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Now, lend me your ears. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.88,0:12:53.33,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,"The Elegy of the Part-Time Worker Who Lost \NHer Identity to the Just-Arrived Newbie."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:15.85,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1234,1)\an4\fnComic Sans MS\fs22\c&HF9FCFF&\3c&HA992FA&\bord3\pos(409.885,259.574)\frz15.71}Thanks for watching,\N everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:15.85,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1152,1)\an4\c&HF9FCFF&\3c&H9D95EC&\bord3\fs20\pos(30,300)}Illustration by Aki Hamaji
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.16,0:13:11.44,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't known each other long,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:14.46,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,but I enjoyed the precious \Ntime we spent together.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.85,0:13:17.47,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan! Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.47,0:13:19.32,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Teach Kita-chan how to do the drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:20.02,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:22.82,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance to restore my good name!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:29.35,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.35,0:13:31.79,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I get nervous when I'm being watched!
