Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.81,0:13:40.71,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.84,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I think I get the idea, \Nso you can rest a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.84,0:13:45.28,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive my arrogance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:47.09,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just glad you\Nweren't seriously hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.61,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.61,0:13:49.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.22,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Her fingertips...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.49,0:13:55.85,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san, what made you want to join a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:14:00.26,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's an indoor activity where \Nyou can be flashy and cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.06,0:14:03.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And I wanna be popular...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My motives are excessively impure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:10.12,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-World peace... I want to \Nwork toward world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:11.99,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,How conscientious!
