Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:16.40,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:25.10,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um, so the senpai you \Nwanted to get closer to...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.10,0:14:25.96,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:27.44,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ryo-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:28.47,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Here ya go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.93,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I have very impure motives.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.88,0:14:40.36,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Senpai playing on the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:41.99,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,and fell head-over-heels for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-san was in another band, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:51.51,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Her above-it-all attitude, her unisex look...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.51,0:14:53.62,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It all makes me squee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:54.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,"Squee"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.38,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,And she just looks so {\i1}right{\i0} \Nholding an instrument!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.38,0:14:59.24,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:02.76,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-When I hold mine, it looks more \Nlike the instrument's holding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.09,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Right? You end up like\Nan appendage to the instrument.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:07.22,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how that happens?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:08.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's like we're best \Nbuddies all of a sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.22,0:15:08.51,DefaultTop,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That's one thing about Ryo-senpai that—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:10.64,Default,Customer,0000,0000,0000,,Um, can I get a cassis orange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.64,0:15:12.53,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Coming right up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:15.51,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, buddies! \NI'll know my place next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.32,0:15:19.52,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,After I heard her play,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:22.37,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I followed Ryo-san's activities for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.37,0:15:24.68,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,and she dropped out of her \Nlast band pretty suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:25.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.82,0:15:28.92,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Then I found out she was \Nrecruiting for Kessoku Band,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:30.75,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,and without thinking, I said I'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.75,0:15:33.53,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Such initiative! Extroversion abounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.78,0:15:36.96,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A band is like your second family, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:38.01,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Family?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.01,0:15:41.37,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you spend more time with them \Nthan with your actual family,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:43.14,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,and you're all chasing the same dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:46.88,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mysterious relationship, \Ncloser than friends or significant others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.37,0:15:49.52,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I've never done clubs or anything similar,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.52,0:15:51.72,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,so I've always wanted to be part of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.72,0:15:53.08,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.08,0:15:55.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted it too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:16:00.08,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I wanted to join Kessoku Band \Nand become Senpai's girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:02.84,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,So much deeper and more \Nintimate than friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.84,0:16:05.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Is Kita-san kind of not-okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.53,0:16:09.28,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But that's all the more reason
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:11.70,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I can't join the band now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:17.57,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I flaked out once already. \NI'm too irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.57,0:16:20.45,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deserve to be in the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:34.38,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3D583C&\pos(320,198.5)}Tickets go on sale at {\c&H25726A&}5 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.08,0:16:30.53,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, good work, all. Feel free to head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.53,0:16:32.46,Default,Nijika Ryo & Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for having us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:34.38,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for having us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.15,0:16:40.28,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for everything today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:42.84,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck with your band!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.84,0:16:44.56,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep rooting for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.56,0:16:45.89,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:47.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:54.82,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.00,0:17:01.72,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Gotoh-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.93,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You're not still worried about me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:07.80,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:11.98,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said before, \NI can't join Kessoku Band.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:15.80,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play guitar, \Nand I already flaked out once...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.80,0:17:18.31,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I... I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.23,0:17:22.39,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I also ran away before the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:24.02,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I hid in a trash can, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.72,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.72,0:17:27.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get you up, Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.69,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:29.69,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.31,0:17:32.32,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kita-san, your left hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.84,0:17:36.96,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You had calluses on your fingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:38.78,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I... I th-think...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.64,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You'd have to be practicing \Nthe guitar pretty hard for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:42.66,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.48,0:17:50.42,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan, we'd love to have you \Nrocking out with us in Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:53.13,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.95,0:17:57.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Because if you hadn't flaked out, \Nwe'd never have met Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:58.93,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:05.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to have a band,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:10.34,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,so I get how it feels intimidating \Nand aspirational at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.34,0:18:11.90,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-So do I!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:16.49,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry. That came out \Nlouder than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:19.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be happy to have her too, right, Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:21.59,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'll only have to pay one-quarter \Nof the studio and quota fees.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.59,0:18:23.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Be a little less honest, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:27.56,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I can be part of Senpai's quota!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:30.38,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So much for that healthy \Nmoving-on thing, I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.06,0:18:34.06,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But I still can't play the guitar...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.06,0:18:34.88,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.44,0:18:37.81,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan will teach you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:38.72,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.72,0:18:40.00,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:40.99,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ehh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.99,0:18:42.02,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.66,0:18:43.93,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:46.77,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't exactly turn her down now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.90,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:58.24,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work really hard to \Nplay guitar in Kessoku Band!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:07.48,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but you should probably give up \Nthat party lifestyle of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.48,0:19:09.46,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,You're dancing like mad\Nevery night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:10.96,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you hear that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:14.06,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it's all mended.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:18.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It came out like a mess, but I'm glad \NI stopped Kita-san from leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I worked really hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.30,0:19:25.78,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I gotta head out now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, don't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.73,0:19:29.98,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're today's MVP!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:33.36,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You're the reason we're back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.36,0:19:34.86,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Gotoh-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.86,0:19:44.78,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\q2\c&H070F0E&\3c&HE8F3F0&\bord1.5\clip(147,0,640,80.19)\move(-2000,35,0,35)}Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me   Praise me
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.20,0:19:39.28,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, well, it was nothing, \Nreally, honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.08,0:19:42.62,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It obviously wasn't nothing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.62,0:19:44.78,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Gotoh-san wears her heart on her sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.19,0:19:49.47,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But I practiced for so long, and yet \NI never really learned how to play guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:51.98,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It just made this quiet 'bum-bum' sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.20,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're sure it wasn't a bass?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:56.45,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm not {\i1}that{\i0} ignorant!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.45,0:19:58.85,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,A bass has four strings, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.76,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,See? It's got the full six strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.83,0:20:06.79,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Some do have six strings...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:08.31,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,That's a six-string bass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:20.03,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kita-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.57,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,It cost me two years' \Nadvance allowance from my dad,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.48,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,not to mention my New Year's money...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:26.15,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Kita-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.70,0:20:33.05,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And so, Kessoku Band officially \Nhad all their members.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.68,0:20:37.50,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,No more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.12,0:20:40.17,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby quit the guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:43.09,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are we breaking up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.44,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Is this one defective too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.44,0:20:46.64,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Did I get another bass?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.51,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's definitely a guitar...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.21,0:20:52.32,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I whine so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.32,0:20:56.09,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're giving up your time after \Nclass and during lunch to teach me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.09,0:20:57.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, it's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.85,0:21:03.24,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,With Ryo-senpai lending me this guitar, \Nand everyone helping... I have to do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.54,0:21:09.07,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-But I really am glad... that Ryo-san \Nb-bought that bass off of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.07,0:21:09.87,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.87,0:21:11.58,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,But when she gave me the money...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.26,0:21:18.04,Flashback,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last of my money, \Nso I'll be eating weeds from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.31,0:21:20.43,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:21.88,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She might have been serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.46,0:21:24.41,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.41,0:21:26.09,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,This one's so hard to hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.09,0:21:28.45,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,The F chord is too hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.40,0:21:32.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That takes me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:34.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I was this way at the start, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.14,0:21:56.83,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-senpai! Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.48,0:21:59.77,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're here early.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:02.18,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She really is eating weeds!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:04.38,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai's so wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.35,0:22:19.80,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,The tune that plays when my loneliness \Nand the pedal are stepped on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:25.35,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Tracks down my cheeks over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.35,0:22:29.01,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,The pounding of my loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.01,0:22:33.11,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Is joined by the rhythm of the snare drum
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.11,0:22:36.20,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,To create a solid pulse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:38.73,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, please remove \Nthe distortion on my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:41.70,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,And take a look inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.70,0:22:45.71,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can get inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.71,0:22:49.21,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the kind of night \Nwhen I hope someone will
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:51.71,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Distortion it's Motion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.71,0:22:55.14,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Once it starts, there's no stopping it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:59.36,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Limits can be overwritten with experience
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:00.70,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.76,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Distortion is always like that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.76,0:23:07.22,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,My heart takes off, outpacing my left brain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.22,0:23:08.86,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Toward where you are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.86,0:23:11.49,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,An escort to the next note
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.49,0:23:14.21,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Distortion on my day-to-day anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:17.05,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,The chord I play when I'm alone at night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.05,0:23:18.51,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the same for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.51,0:23:21.13,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,I spent all those days chasing my ideal image
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.13,0:23:25.27,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Play an F chord with distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.27,0:23:29.31,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,So loud that the needle swings off the scale
